name: cult2mgs_names

name: culturable_species
label: List with culturable species
description: Species names which can be cultured

name: cultured_species
label: Cultured species data
description: Per sample (TIMID id) the number of times a certain species has been cultured

name: mgs_culturable_species
label: Mapping of mgs species names to culturable species names

name: mgs_cultured_data

name: mgs_species_data
label: Metagenomics species data
description: Per sample (TIMID id) the species that have been detected with abundance cut off

name: oxygen_requirements
label: Oxygen requirements
description: List with the oxygen requirement categories

name: sample_info
label: TIMID sample information
description: General information of the TIMID sample

name: species_oxygen_cultured_counts
label: Culture frequency by oxygen level
description: Per sample and mgs_species the culture frequency by oxygen level
